                            <comment id="16159520" author="hossman" created="Fri, 8 Sep 2017 23:35:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;similar looking failures have happened on 2 diff policeman jenkins (master) builds today...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jenkins.thetaphi.de/job/Lucene-Solr-7.0-Windows/139/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://jenkins.thetaphi.de/job/Lucene-Solr-7.0-Windows/139/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
