                            <comment id="16159522" author="hossman" created="Fri, 8 Sep 2017 23:38:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;failure log from my local machine.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16159529" author="hossman" created="Fri, 8 Sep 2017 23:47:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Appears to have been caused by the refactoring in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-10990&quot; title=&quot;QueryComponent.process breakup (for readability)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-10990&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-10990&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;assigning to christine for review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16159965" author="cpoerschke" created="Sat, 9 Sep 2017 14:43:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Hoss for creating this ticket! I was able to reproduce with the seed. Attaching patch with fix. The root cause is that the ResponseBuilder&apos;s getQueryCommand method is in fact a createQueryCommand method. (Would propose to separately rename getQueryCommand to createQueryCommand with a deprecated delegating getQueryCommand method kept around for convenience on the branch_7x branch only.)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16161645" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 11 Sep 2017 17:33:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 37b8ac6ff5efc68a4637ddb65c7c15faef21227a in lucene-solr&apos;s branch refs/heads/master from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cpoerschke&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cpoerschke&quot;&gt;cpoerschke&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=lucene-solr.git;h=37b8ac6&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=lucene-solr.git;h=37b8ac6&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11343&quot; title=&quot;reproducible failures from TestSegmentSorting.testSegmentTerminateEarly on master&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-11343&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-11343&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: fix TestSegmentSorting.testSegmentTerminateEarly test failure caused by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-10990&quot; title=&quot;QueryComponent.process breakup (for readability)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-10990&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-10990&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16161676" author="cpoerschke" created="Mon, 11 Sep 2017 17:48:43 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;... to separately rename getQueryCommand to createQueryCommand ...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11349&quot; title=&quot;rename ResponseBuilder&amp;#39;s getQueryCommand to createQueryCommand&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-11349&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-11349&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; created for this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
